"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Documents Required</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">:</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">1)&nbsp;&nbsp; Visa application form to be filled out in English or Croatian language and signed by the applicant</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">.</span> </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">2)&nbsp;&nbsp; Valid Passport - minimum of three months, Clear Photocopy of front and last page and used pages (Current passport and last 02 old passports)</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">3)&nbsp; Two photographs: please see the information on the Photo Specification page.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">) </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Travel health insurance.&nbsp; The insurance must be valid for 30 days from the date of travel.</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&qu