pan></strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#202122\">&nbsp;is a country in&nbsp;Central&nbsp;and&nbsp;Eastern Europe&nbsp;which borders&nbsp;Bulgaria&nbsp;to the south,&nbsp;Ukraine&nbsp;to the north,&nbsp;Hungary&nbsp;to the west,&nbsp;Serbia&nbsp;to the southwest,&nbsp;Moldova&nbsp;to the east, and the&nbsp;Black Sea&nbsp;to the southeast. It has an area of 238,397&nbsp;km&nbsp;(92,046&nbsp;sq&nbsp;mi), with a population of around 19 million. Romania is the&nbsp;sixth-most populous&nbsp;member state of the&nbsp;European Union. Its capital and largest city are&nbsp;<strong>Bucharest</strong>. The <strong>Leu</strong>&nbsp;is the currency of Romania.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#202122\">Romania is a&nbsp;developing country, with a&nbsp;high-income economy,&nbsp;ranking 49th in the&nbsp;Human Development Index. It has the world&#39;s&nbsp;45th&nbsp;largest economy by nominal GDP, and following rapid economic growth in the early 2000s, the country has an economy based predominantly on services and is a producer and net exporter of machines and electric energy through companies. Romania has been a member of the <strong>United Nations</strong> since 1955,&nbsp;<strong>NATO</strong>&nbsp;since 2004, and the <strong>European Union</strong> since 2007. </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#003366\">Work/Long-Stay Visa&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Short Stay Visa&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Visit Visa&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Business Visa</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\"><span style=\"color:#365f91\"><span style=\"font-size:36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#003366\">Work / Long-stay Visa</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#565656\">With the exception of the work permit for seconded workers, the long-stay visa for employment is granted to third-country nationals on the grounds of the work permit issued by the General Immigration Inspectorate of the Ministry of Interior of Romania, in accordance with the legislation in force.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#565656\">The visa application must be submitted along with the following Supporting Documents:</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">1) Passport valid at least three months beyond the validity of visa;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">2) NID card copy</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">3) 2 recent color photos 3 cm x 4 cm, on a white background;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">4) 10) The criminal record (Police Clearance Certificate) issued by the authorities from the country of domicile or residence, apostilled or legalized, as the case may be;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">5) Dully filled in the application form.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">6) letter of recommendation from the recruiting agency;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">7) Booking of a two-way flight ticket to Romania;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">8) Medical insurance valid in Romania, </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">9) Copy of the work permit issued by the General Immigration Inspectorate of the Ministry of Interior of Romania;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">10) The proof of the means of subsistence at the level of the minimum guaranteed wage for the entire period specified on the visa;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">11) The criminal record (Police Clearance Certificate) issued by the authorities from the country of domicile or residence, apostilled or legalized, as the case may be;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">12) Proof of accommodation.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">13)&nbsp; Visa fee</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Cambria,serif\"><span style=\"color:#365f91\"><span style=\"font-size:36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#003366\">Short Stay Visa</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#565656\">Supporting documents:</span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">1)&nbsp; Passport valid at least three months beyond the intended period of stay</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">2)&nbsp; NID card copy</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">3)&nbsp; 2 recent color photos 3 cm x 4 cm, on a white background;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">4)&nbsp; Dully filled in the application form </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">5)&nbsp; Invitation approved by the inspectorate general for immigration &ndash; Ministry of Internal Affairs of Romania,</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">OR,</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Valid visa/residence permit issued by a state the citizens of which are not required a visa to enter Romani;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">6)&nbsp; Letter of certification of employment;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">7)&nbsp; Booking of a two-way flight ticket to Romania;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">8)&nbsp; Medical insurance valid in Romania, </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=