serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a) Six (6) months bank statement (saving and current a/c, as applicable), and</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; b) Three years Income Tax returns (personal and company, as applicable), and</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; c) Copy of international credit card with three months credit card statement and</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;d) Endorsement on passport/receipt of purchase of foreign exchange</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">10)&nbsp;&nbsp; Proof of&nbsp;current social and professional status:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font