nbsp;in the&nbsp;Mediterranean Sea. It lies south of&nbsp;Italy, east of&nbsp;Tunisia, and north of&nbsp;Libya. With a population of about 515,000 over an area of 316 km, Malta is the world&#39;s tenth smallest country in the area. Its capital is&nbsp;Valletta, which is the smallest national capital in the&nbsp;European Union. It has been a member state of the&nbsp;Commonwealth of Nations&nbsp;and the&nbsp;United Nations&nbsp;since independence, and joined the&nbsp;European Union&nbsp;in 2004; it became part of the&nbsp;Eurozone&nbsp;monetary union in 2008.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#548dd4\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Tourist&nbsp; Visa&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Work&nbsp; Visa&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Business Visa&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#548dd4\">Tourist&nbsp; Visa</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">1)&nbsp; &nbsp;Visa application form:&nbsp;to be filled out in English. </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">2)&nbsp; &nbsp;Valid Passport&nbsp;- It must be valid for at least another six (6) months starting from the day traveler depart from Malta (Current passport and old passports)</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">3)&nbsp;&nbsp; Two photographs (white background, without border).</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">4)&nbsp;&nbsp; Travel health insurance.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">5)&nbsp; &nbsp;Proof of&nbsp;residence&nbsp;for nationals: a photocopy of the stay permit.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">6)&nbsp; Cover letter:&nbsp;explaining the purpose of the trip with itinerary detailed location(s) and duration of stay.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;7)&nbsp; Transportation&nbsp;return travel air ticket. </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">8)&nbsp; Proof of the&nbsp;purpose of stay&nbsp;in Malta:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a)&nbsp; Proof of Hotel Booking Payment.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; b)&nbsp; Certificate of a paid tourist package.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; c) Day-to-day itinerary with ensured accommodation for the entire stay.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; d)&nbsp; Complete Malta telephone contact and address for all accommodations.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">Kindly note that the applications for Malta tourist visas for tourist visits are processed as per the actual plan of travel and stay. Any change in the travel plan, cancellation/change of accommodations, etc. after submission of the application will lead to delay in the processing of the application. Similar changes after issuance of visa (if approved) for the Republic of Malta might lead to revocation of visa.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">9)&nbsp;&nbsp; Proof of sufficient funds:&nbsp;Traveler must be able to prove that traveler can sustain financially for the duration of trip:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a) Six (6) months bank statement (saving and current a/c, as applicable).</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; b) Copy of international credit card with six (6) months credit card statement. </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;c) Endorsement on passport/receipt of purchase of foreign exchange.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">10)&nbsp;&nbsp; Proof of&nbsp;current social and professional status:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">Marriage Certificate, Birth Certificate of children&rsquo;s, etc.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a) Service &ndash; Letter issued by the employer on company&rsquo;s official letterhead establishing position of the employee in the company, years in service, grant of leave, last six (6) months salary slip, ID card, visiting card. </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; b) Business/self-employed &ndash; Visa request letter on official letterhead with company registration papers, etc.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; c) Student &ndash; Letter from school/university for grant of leave and copy of the valid ID.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">Please note that you may be required to come for a personal interview with the visa officer at the Embassy of the Republic of Malta prior to a decision being made on your application.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">The documents attached shall not be older than&nbsp;three&nbsp;(3) months.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">The Embassy of Malta may require you to submit additional supporting documents and/or certified translation as well as the international certification (apostille) of the documents during the visa application process.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#548dd4\">Work&nbsp; Visa</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">Documents Required:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">1)&nbsp;&nbsp; Visa application form to be filled out in English. </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">2)&nbsp;&nbsp; Valid Passport - minimum of three months, Clear Photocopy of front and last page and used pages (Current passport and old passports).</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">3)&nbsp; Two photographs (white background, without border).</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">4) </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">Travel health insurance.&nbsp; The insurance must be valid for 30 days from the date of travel.<br />\r\n5)&nbsp;&nbsp; Cover letter: explaining the purpose of the trip with itinerary detailed location(s) and duration of stay in Malta.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">6)&nbsp;&nbsp; Confirmed departure flight reservation - one way ( ticket should be valid for 15 days from the date of submission).</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">7)&nbsp; Copy of work permit.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">8)&nbsp; Visa fee.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#548dd4\">Business Visa</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">Documents Required:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">1)&nbsp; Visa application form:&nbsp;to be filled out in English.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">2)&nbsp; Valid Passport&nbsp;- It must be valid for at least another six (6) months starting from the day traveler&nbsp;depart from Malta. </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">3)&nbsp;&nbsp; Two photographs: (white background, without border).</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">4)&nbsp;&nbsp; Travel health insurance.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">5)&nbsp;&nbsp; Proof of&nbsp;residence&nbsp;for nationals: a photocopy of the stay permit.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">6)&nbsp;&nbsp; Cover letter: explaining the purpose of the trip with itinerary detailed location(s) and duration of stay in Malta.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">7)&nbsp;&nbsp; Means of&nbsp;transportation&nbsp;return travel tickets for airplanes.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">8)&nbsp;&nbsp; Proof of the&nbsp;purpose of stay&nbsp;in Malta:<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a)&nbsp; Proof of Hotel Booking Payment.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; b)&nbsp; Certificate of a paid tourist package.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; c) Day-to-day itinerary with ensured accommodation for the entire stay.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; d)&nbsp; Complete Malta telephone contact and address for all accommodations.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">9)&nbsp;&nbsp; Letter of Guarantee by Legal Person: in original or copy if the original is deposited at the Ministry of Foreign and European Affairs in Malta; with the Letter of Guarantee, the guarantor shall enclose proof of solvency (BON 1 or BON 2 Forms, or a confirmation of the Commercial Court that it is not in liquidation, etc.); the applicant shall be handed a photocopy of the Letter of Guarantee.</span></span></span></span></span></span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">10) </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">Documents proving&nbsp;sufficient funds&nbsp;to support the stay in Malta and to return to the state of residence or to travel to a third state.</span></span></span></span></span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">Exceptionally, if the Letter of Guarantee/Invitation Letter indicates the guarantor is fully accepting all the expenses related to visiting and departing from Malta, the applicant can be exempt from the requirement to present the proof of sufficient funds.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe supporting documents may include:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">a)&nbsp; Six (6) months bank statement (saving and current a/c, as applicable), </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">b)&nbsp; Three years Income Tax returns (personal and company, as applicable), </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">c)&nbsp; Copy of international credit card with three months credit card statement and</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">d)&nbsp; Endorsement on passport/receipt of purchase of foreign exchange</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">Proof of&nbsp;current social and professional status:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">a)&nbsp; Service &ndash; Letter issued by the employer on company&rsquo;s official letterhead establishing position of the employee in the company, years in service, grant of leave and salary certificate of the last three (3) months</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">b)&nbsp; Business/self-employed &ndash; Visa request letter on official letterhead with company registration papers.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">Accommodation:&nbsp;hotel booking, private or other accommodation, real estate title deed or lease, proof of ownership or lease of a boat, etc. Accommodation can be provided by the guarantor or the inviting party if so indicated in the Letter of Guarantee or the Letter of Invitation.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">Proof of sufficient Funds:</span></span></span></span></span></span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">Three months bank statements (savings and current a/c, as applicable) in Original &ndash; duly signed and stamped by an authorized official of the respective bank.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">The documents attached shall not be older than&nbsp;three (3)&nbsp;months.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">The Embassy of Malta may require you to submit additional supporting documents and/or certified translation as well as the international certification (apostille) of the documents during the visa application process.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">Please note that you may be required to come for a personal interview with the visa officer at the Embassy of the Republic of Malta prior to a decision being made on your application</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">আমাদের সেবাসমূহঃ</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#0070c0\">১) ভ্রমণ সহায়তা</span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#0070c0\">২) ভিসা পরামর্শ</span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#0070c0\">৩) প্রক্রিয়া বিষয়ক সহায়তা</span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#0070c0\">৪) আমদানি&ndash;রপ্তানি ব্যবসা পরামর্শ</span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">মাল্টা</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">, সরকারিভাবে &ldquo;মাল্টা প্রজাতন্ত্র&rdquo; নামে পরিচিত ভূমধ্য সাগরে অবস্থিত একটি দক্ষিণ ইউরোপীয় দ্বীপ দেশ।&nbsp; এই দ্বীপ দেশটি ইতালির দক্ষিণে, তিউনিশিয়ার পূর্বে এবং লিবিয়ার উত্তরে অবস্থিত। ৩১৬ কিমি এলাকা জুড়ে প্রায় বিস্তৃত এবং ৫,১৫,০০০ জনসংখ্যার অধ্যুষিত মাল্টা বিশ্বের দশম ক্ষুদ্রতম দেশ। এর রাজধানী হল ভ্যাল্টা, যা ইউরোপীয় ইউনিয়নের ক্ষুদ্রতম জাতীয় রাজধানী। মাল্টা স্বাধীনতার পর থেকে কমনওয়েলথ অফ নেশনস এবং জাতিসংঘের সদস্য রাষ্ট্র, এবং ২০০৪ সালে ইউরোপীয় ইউনিয়নে যোগদান করে এবং ২০০৮ সালে ইউরোজোন মুদ্রা ইউনিয়নের অংশ হয়ে ওঠে।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#548dd4\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ভ্রমণ ভিসা </span></span></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:20.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#548dd4\">চাকুরী ভিসা&nbsp;</span></span></span>&nbsp;</strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:20.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#548dd4\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></strong><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:20.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#548dd4\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ব্যবসা ভিসা</span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#548dd4\">ভ্রমণ ভিসা&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">প্রয়োজনীয় কাগজপত্রের তালিকা:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">১) ভিসা আবেদনপত্র ইংরেজি ভাষায় পূরণ করতে হব এবং আবেদনকারী দ্বারা স্বাক্ষরিত হতে হবে।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">২)&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">মাল্টায়</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">ভ্রমণ শেষ হওয়ার পরেও কমপক্ষে ছয় (৬) মাস মেয়াদ </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">সম্পন্ন</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> পাসপোর্ট</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">, &nbsp;আবেদনকারীর তথ্য সংবলিত প্রথম, শেষ এবং ব্যবহৃত পৃষ্ঠার পরিষ্কার ছায়ালিপি। (বর্তমান এবং মেয়াদউত্তীর্ণ পুরাতন পাসপোর্ট) </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">৩) ২টি সাম্প্রতিক রঙিন ছবি (৩ সেমি </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">x৪ সেমি, &nbsp;সাদা পটভূমিতে)।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">৪) </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">মাল্টার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">জন্য বৈধ চিকিৎসা বীমা।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">৫) নিজ দেশ ছাড়া অন্য দেশে নাগরিকদের বসবাসের প্রমাণ, ভিন্ন দেশে অবস্থান করার অনুমতিপত্রের ছায়ালিপি। </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">৬) </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">মাল্টায়</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">ভ্রমণের উদ্দেশ্য, সম্ভাব্য </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">আবাসস্থান</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">গুলো এবং অবস্থানের সময়সীমা ইত্যাদির উল্লেখসহ একটি পরিচিতি পত্র।</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">৭) </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">মাল্টায়</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">ভ্রমণের জন্য নিশ্চিত করা উড়োজাহাজে আসা-যাওয়ার টিকিট।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">৮) </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">মাল্টায়</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">অবস্থানের উদ্দেশ্য প্রমাণের জন্য কাগজপত্রদিঃ</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; ক) হোটেলে অবস্থানের উদ্দ্যেশে অগ্রিম ভাড়া প্রদান ও নিবন্ধনের প্রমাণ।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; খ) ভ্রমণের জন্য নিবন্ধিত পর্যটন সংস্থা হতে সেবা গ্রহণের সনদ। </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; গ) ভ্রমণকালীন প্রতিদিনের ভ্রমণ সংক্রান্ত পরিকল্পনা ও আবাসনের প্রমান।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; ঘ) </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">মাল্টায়</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">অবস্থানকালীন সব আবাসনের বিস্তারিত ঠিকানা এবং টেলিফোন নাম্বার। </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">এখানে উল্ল্যেখ্য যে, পর্যটকদের ভ্রমণের জন্য </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">মাল্টায়</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">ভিসার আবেদনগুল</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">ো</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> ভ্রমণ এবং অবস্থানের প্রকৃত পরিকল্পনা অনুযায়ী প্রক্রিয়া করা হয়। ভিসা আবেদন জমা দেওয়ার পর ভ্রমণ পরিকল্পনার কোন পরিবর্তন</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">, &nbsp;বাতিল/বাসস্থান পরিবর্তন ইত্যাদি আবেদনের প্রক্রিয়ায় বিলম্ব ঘটবে। </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">মাল্টায়</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">ভ্রমণের জন্য ভিসা জারির পর যদি অনুরূপ পরিবর্তন হয় (যদি অনুমোদিত হয়) তাহলে সংশ্লিষ্ট কর্তৃপক্ষ উক্ত ভিসা প্রত্যাহার করতে পারে।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">৯)&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">মাল্টায় </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">অবস্থান, ভ্রমণ এবং নিজ মাতৃভুমিতে বা তৃতীয় রাজ্যে ফিরে যেতে পর্যাপ্ত আর্থিক স্বচ্ছলতা প্রমাণের জন্য প্রয়োজনীয় কাগজপত্রাদিঃ </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ক) সর্বশেষ ছয় </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">(৬)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> মাসের ব্যাংক</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> লেনদেনের প্রমাণপত্র।</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">খ) সর্বশেষ তিন বছরের আয়কর রিটার্ন (ব্যক্তিগত এবং কোম্পানি, প্রযোজ্য ক্ষেত্রে)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">।</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">গ) সর্বশেষ তিন মাসের ক্রেডিট কার্ড স্টেটমেন্টসহ আন্তর্জাতিক ক্রেডিট কার্ডের কপি</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">।</span></span> &nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">ঘ) বৈদেশিক মুদ্রা ক্রয়ের রশিদ/ পাসপোর্টে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> নিবন্ধনের </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">প্রমান</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">। </span></span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">১০)&nbsp; বর্তমান সামাজিক এবং পেশাগত অবস্থার প্রমাণের জন্য কাগজপত্রাদিঃ</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">বিবাহের সনদ, সন্তানের জন্ম সনদ, ইত্যাদি।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">ক)চাকুরী</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">জীবী </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">- প্রতিষ্ঠান/কোম্পানির </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">সরকার অনুমোদিত</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">নাম, ঠিকানাযুক্ত পত্রে নিয়োগকর্তা কর্তৃক জারি করা চিঠিতে উক্ত কর্মচারীর প্রতিষ্ঠান/কোম্পানিতে পদমর্যাদা, &nbsp;চাকরিতে যোগদানের সময়</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">, ভ্রমণকালীন &nbsp;ছুটি মঞ্জুরির সম্মতি এবং বিগত ছয় (৬) মাসের বেতন </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">প্রদানের </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">সনদ।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">খ) ব্যবসায়ী/স্বনির্ভর - কোম্পানির নিবন্ধন কাগজপত্রসহ </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">সরকার অনুমোদিত</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">নাম, ঠিকানাযুক্ত পত্রে ভিসার জন্য অনুরোধ পত্র। </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">গ) ছাত্র - ছুটির মঞ্জুরির জন্য স্কুল/বিশ্ববিদ্যালয় থেকে চিঠি এবং স্কুল/বিশ্ববিদ্যালয়ের বৈধ পরিচয় পত্রের ছায়ালিপি</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">।</span></span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">১১) ভিসার খরচ। </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">*ভিসা আবেদনের সাথে সংযুক্ত কাগজপত্রাদি তিন </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">(৩)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> মাসের বেশি পুরাতন হতে পারবে না।*</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">মাল্টা</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> দূতাবাস প্রদত্ত নির্দেশনা মোতাবেক আবেদনকারী ভিসা গ্রহণের জন্য সাক্ষাৎকার প্রদান করবেন এবং ভিসা আবেদন প্রক্রিয়ার সময় </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">মাল্টা</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> দূতাবাসের চাহিদা মোতাবেক অন্যান্য সহায়ক কাগজপত্র অথবা সত্যায়িত অনুবাদের পাশাপাশি </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">বিভিন্ন </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">কাগজপত্র আন্তর্জাতিক মান অনুযায়ী (অ্যাপোস্টিল) আবেদনপত্রের সাথে প্রদান করবেন।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#548dd4\">চাকুরী ভিসা&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">প্রয়োজনীয় কাগজপত্রের তালিকা:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">১) ভিসা আবেদনপত্র ইংরেজি &nbsp;ভাষায় পূরণ করতে হবে এবং আবেদনকারী দ্বারা স্বাক্ষরিত হতে হবে।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">২) কমপক্ষে তিন মাস মেয়াদের পাসপোর্ট</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">, &nbsp;আবেদনকারীর তথ্য সংবলিত প্রথম, শেষ এবং ব্যবহৃত পৃষ্ঠার পরিষ্কার ফটোকপি। (বর্তমান এবং মেয়াদউত্তীর্ণ পুরাতন পাসপোর্ট) </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">৩) ২টি সাম্প্রতিক রঙিন ছবি (৩ সেমি </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">x ৪ সেমি, &nbsp;সাদা পটভূমিতে)।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">৪) </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">মাল্টা</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">র</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> জন্য বৈধ চিকিৎসা বীমা</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> (মাল্টা আগমনের তারিখ হইতে ৩০ দিন পর্যন্ত মেয়াদ সম্পন্ন) </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">৫) </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">মাল্টা</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">র</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> ভ্রমণের 