y&nbsp;in the&nbsp;Mediterranean Sea. It lies south of&nbsp;Italy, east of&nbsp;Tunisia, and north of&nbsp;Libya. With a population of about 515,000 over an area of 316 km, Malta is the world&#39;s tenth smallest country in the area. Its capital is&nbsp;Valletta, which is the smallest national capital in the&nbsp;European Union. It has been a member state of the&nbsp;Commonwealth of Nations&nbsp;and the&nbsp;United Nations&nbsp;since independence, and joined the&nbsp;European Union&nbsp;in 2004; it became part of the&nbsp;Eurozone&nbsp;monetary union in 2008.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#548dd4\">Tourist&nbsp; Visa&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Work&nbsp; Visa &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"#BUSINESS\">&nbsp;Business Visa&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#548dd4\">Tourist&nbsp; Visa</span></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">1)&nbsp; &nbsp;Visa application form:&nbsp;to be filled out in English. </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&q